    body: `S.C Roofing carries out the full range of chimney repairs across Bath. We repoint with lime mortar on pre-1919 properties, replacing decayed joints like-for-like to prevent moisture ingress and thermal cracking. Lead step flashings and back gutters are hand-dressed on site to the Lead Sheet Association standard. Where stacks have become structurally unstable, we rebuild from below the roofline using reclaimed Bath stone or matching brick. Drone surveys are available for high or difficult-access chimneys.`,
