    metaDescription: `Guttering, fascias and soffits in Frome, BA11. UPVC and cast iron. Local contractor. SC Roofing 07881 903 188.`,
    intro: `Frome's mix of old stone and modern housing requires different approaches to roofline. On the town's older properties — particularly in the conservation area — cast iron guttering is the appropriate material, fitting with the character of the street and avoiding planning complications.`,
    body: `S.C Roofing supplies and fits cast iron half-round guttering and downpipes for period Frome properties, and UPVC systems for modern homes. Fascias and soffits are replaced or added where required. We install ventilated soffits on all new installations where Building Regulations require roof space ventilation.`,
